*ibm-jdk-1.3.1-r1 (12 May 2002)
  06 Sep 2002; Owen Stampflee <owen@gentoo.org> :
  Added "." to the CLASSPATH in the env.d scripts.

  01 Sep 2002; Karl Trygve Kalleberg <karltk@gentoo.org> ibm-jdk-1.3.1-r1.ebuild:
  Fixed typo that prevented java-config from recognizing the installed
  VM. Fixes #7241.
 
  26 Aug 2002; Karl Trygve Kalleberg <karltk@gentoo.org> ibm-jdk-1.3.1-r1.ebuild:
  Added doc keyword to optionally install documentation. Set slot to 1.3, so
  it can coexist with other IBM JDKs (if they come). Fixes #6668. Now
  provides virtual/jre-1.3.1, virtual/jdk-1.3.1.

  01 Aug 2002; Karl Trygve Kalleberg <karltk@gentoo.org> ibm-jdk-1.3.1-r1.ebuild:
  Added LICENSE, KEYWORDS and SLOT.

  14 May 2002; Karl Trygve Kalleberg <karltk@gentoo.org> ibm-jdk-1.3.1-r1.ebuild files/digest-ibm-jdk-1.3.1-r1:
  Fixed the creation of a spurious /usr/ibm-jdk-1.3.1/share.

  12 May 2002; Karl Trygve Kalleberg <karltk@gentoo.org> ibm-jdk-1.3.1-r1.ebuild, files/digest-ibm-jdk-1.3.1-r1:
  Disabled browser plugin as it does not work.
  Removed ibm-jdk-1.3.1.ebuild, files/digest-ibm-jdk-1.3.1

*ibm-jdk-1.3.0-r4 (12 May 2002)

  26 Aug 2002; Karl Trygve Kalleberg <karltk@gentoo.org> ibm-jdk-1.3.0-r4.ebuild:
  Added doc keyword to optionally install documentation.

  14 May 2002; Karl Trygve Kalleberg <karltk@gentoo.org> ibm-jdk-1.3.0-r4.ebuild files/digest-ibm-jdk-1.3.0-r4:
  Fixed the creation of a spurious /usr/ibm-jdk-1.3.0/share.

  12 May 2002; Karl Trygve Kalleberg <karltk@gentoo.org> ibm-jdk-1.3.0-r4.ebuild files/digest-ibm-jdk-1.3.0-r4:
  Disabled browser plugin as it does not work.
  Removed ibm-jdk-1.3.0-r3.ebuild files/digest-ibm-jdk-1.3.0-r3

*ibm-jdk-1.3.1 (10 Apr 2002)

  10 Apr 2002; Karl Trygve Kalleberg <karltk@gentoo.org> ibm-jdk-1.3.1.ebuild files/digest-ibm-jdk-1.3.1 files/ibm-jdk-1.3.1:
  New upstream version. Enhancement request submitted by Nuno Ferreira
  <nuno.m.r.f@mail.telepac.pt>.

*ibm-jdk-1.3.0-r3 (09 Apr 2002)

  09 Apr 2002; Karl Trygve Kalleberg <karltk@gentoo.org> ibm-jdk-1.3.0-r3.ebuild files/digest-ibm-jdk-1.3.0-r3:
  Now sets proper ROOTPATH.
  Removed ibm-jdk-1.3.0-r2.ebuild files/digest-ibm-jdk-1.3.0-r2

*ibm-jdk-1.3.0-r2 (18 Mar 2002)

  18 Mar 2002; G.Bevin <karkt@gentoo.org> files/digest-ibm-jdk-1.3.0-r2 ibm-jdk-1.3.0-r2.ebuild files/ibm-jdk-1.3.0 :
  Added support for JVM switching.
  Removed old revisions.

*ibm-jdk-1.3.0-r1 (7 Feb 2002)

  1 Feb 2002; G.Bevin <gbevin@gentoo.org> files/digest-ibm-jdk-1.3.0-r1 ibm-jdk-1.3.0-r1.ebuild :
  IBM JDK now tells Portage that it provides a virtual/jdk-1.3 and 
  virtual/jre-1.3. This means that is a proper Blackdown/Sun replacement for
  those who prefer the IBM JDK.

*ibm-jdk-1.3.0 (1 Feb 2002)

  1 Feb 2002; G.Bevin <gbevin@gentoo.org> ChangeLog :
  Added initial ChangeLog.
